# Runtime state is PII (contacted emails, do-not-contact list, candidate jobs) and secrets
# (encrypted API keys). Deny the whole directory and re-admit only the committed samples —
# an allowlist here drifts the moment a new state file is added, and the failure mode is
# baking real personal emails into a pushed image layer forever.
data/*
!data/*.example.json
